<br>
Make the situation challenging in other ways.<br>
<br>
Second, This is NOT an applicable argument to TLC.<br>
<br>
TLC is not really appropriate any longer on FV, it is only here to help shield us from the d00ds and farmers. It hurts the server economy (as blisteringly bad as it is already), it hurts people who retro-complete quests, and it hurts the spirit of the game.<br>
